				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: This or That?<a name="68753"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Nov 2 04 9:41 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I'll take a chance that the other AAs you have don't fall into the advanced defensive category, and you'd really like to continue your &quot;tank kiting&quot; activities for an extended period.
<br />

<br />
Finish your Defensive AAs next.  Get Lightning Reflexes to 4, then Physical Enhancement, then Combat Stability 3, and then Improved Defense to 4.  You'll hold up a lot better in a melee fight.
<br />

<br />
Consider switching your weapons around or getting a better primary weapon for when you're doing this (or add an LDoN aug to the BDMG) and then add 2-3 levels of Weapon Affinity.
<br />

<br />
End result:  You'll be taking significantly less damage and taking them down faster.
<br />

<br />
Good luck !!</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
