With BDMG and Copper Hammer  I am at 1653 DPM (including the proc from the Hammer)
<br />

<br />
If I use TWO Copper hammers I get 1810 DPM 
<br />

<br />
If I use a Delightful Orb of forgotten Magic and a C Hammer I get 1811 DPM (I think the orb goes for under 10k)
<br />

<br />
