Gratz on 70 Bud!
<br />

<br />
Now my reply to this post:
<br />

<br />
I am just curious on something here.
<br />

<br />
All things considered, you are talking about apx 1800DPM Damage per minute per weapon? This equates to approximately 60DPS Damage per second (3600DPM / 60sec = 60).
<br />

<br />
Your are a Bard right?
<br />

<br />
Thunderous Drums of Karana in Primary Hand, doing a 4-chant at 64 (41pt DoT x 2.6Mod = 106ea. x 4 = 424 / 6sec = 70DPS)
<br />
or in DPM terms +600DPM. I just don't get the tanking bit as SoE refuses to let us even come close to Ranger DPS <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-9.gif" border="0" alt="Crying" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
Personally, I swarm kite in PoN when I have a spare 30min to an hour. I can typically notch and AA per hour there with the WW camp (and grabbing vicinity trash when I run out of them). Plus I typically get 3-5 diamonds in an hour of mixed variety. Therefore you're looking at 1k and 1AA in about an hour. That's if you keep moving. With a 1yr old and 3yr old, I've slowed down to and AA and 1K every 2 hours, but that was one-handed. <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-4.gif" border="0" alt="Tongue out" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
Food for thought!
<br />

<br />
Gratz again Drumm!
