<br />

<br />
When you're interupted, fizzling 5-6 in a row trying to get the next song off and watching your effects fade because of it and your HP bar dropping you'll be thinking about how LR et al. could have given you more chance to dodge a hit = more chance to keep twisting along = less damage taken = more fun in the long run.
<br />

